remarks: Lemma for ~ nodense .  Give a condition for surreal less than when two surreals have the same birthday.  (Contributed by Scott Fenton, 19-Jun-2011.)
statement:
nodenselem8 $p |- ( ( A e. No /\ B e. No /\ ( bday ` A ) = ( bday ` B ) ) -> ( A <s B <-> ( ( A ` |^| { a e. On | ( A ` a ) =/= ( B ` a ) } ) = 1o /\ ( B ` |^| { a e. On | ( A ` a ) =/= ( B ` a ) } ) = 2o ) ) ) $.
$d A a $.
$d B a $.
